---
import MainLayout from '../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
import { Icon } from 'astro-icon/components';
---
<MainLayout title="Intelligent Video Recorder | spot.ai IVR — Blue Cap IT" description="The spot.ai Intelligent Video Recorder combines hardware, software, and AI analytics in one appliance. Supports up to 32 cameras with 30-90 day local storage, deep-learning models, and hybrid cloud access.">
  <div class="inner-hero">
    <div class="section-inner">
      <img src="/spotai/spotai-logo.png" alt="spot.ai" style="max-height:50px;width:auto;margin-bottom:1.5rem;"/>
      <img src="/images/spotai-ivr-hero.jpg" alt="Server rack with blinking green status lights representing video storage hardware" style="width:100%;height:auto;max-height:340px;object-fit:cover;border-radius:1rem;margin-bottom:2rem;box-shadow:0 8px 32px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);" />
      <div class="crumbs"><a href="index.html">Home</a> <span>/</span> <a href="spotai.html">spot.ai</a> <span>/</span> Intelligent Video Recorder</div>
      <div class="section-label">spot.ai Hardware</div>
      <h1>Intelligent <span class="grad">Video Recorder</span></h1>
      <p class="section-sub">The brain of the spot.ai platform. The IVR combines purpose-built hardware, AI-powered software, and deep-learning analytics in one compact appliance. It auto-discovers cameras, encrypts and stores footage locally, and runs AI models at the edge — with cloud access for remote viewing and management.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <section>
    <div class="section-inner">
      <div class="why-grid">
        <div>
          <div class="section-label">Why the IVR</div>
          <h2>Not Just an NVR.<br/><span class="grad">An AI Engine.</span></h2>
          <p class="section-sub">Traditional NVRs just record and store video. The spot.ai Intelligent Video Recorder does that — plus runs deep-learning AI models on every frame, indexes footage for instant search, monitors camera health, and connects to the cloud for remote access. It's a complete, out-of-the-box video intelligence solution.</p>
          <div style="margin-top:2rem;display:flex;gap:1rem;flex-wrap:wrap;">
            <a href="contact.html" class="btn-primary">Get a Free Quote</a>
            <a href="tel:4108584031" class="btn-ghost">Call (410) 858-4031</a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <ul class="why-list">
          <li class="why-item">
            <div class="why-icon"><Icon name="lucide:database" /></div>
            <div><h4>30-90 Day Local Storage</h4><p>Built-in NVR redundancy with 30, 60, or 90-day local storage options. Your footage is always available, even if internet goes down.</p></div>
          </li>
          <li class="why-item">
            <div class="why-icon"><Icon name="lucide:camera" /></div>
            <div><h4>Up to 32 Cameras</h4><p>Each IVR appliance supports up to 32 cameras — and scales seamlessly across multiple appliances for larger deployments.</p></div>
          </li>
          <li class="why-item">
            <div class="why-icon"><Icon name="lucide:brain" /></div>
            <div><h4>Edge AI Processing</h4><p>Deep-learning models run directly on the IVR — no cloud dependency for real-time detection, classification, and alerting.</p></div>
          </li>
          <li class="why-item">
            <div class="why-icon"><Icon name="lucide:wrench" /></div>
            <div><h4>Zero-Touch Setup</h4><p>Auto-discovers cameras on the network, ingests video streams, and begins AI indexing immediately. No manual configuration required.</p></div>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section>
    <div class="section-inner" style="text-align:center;padding:4rem 1.5rem;">
      <h2>Replace Your NVR <span class="grad">With Intelligence</span></h2>
      <p class="section-sub" style="max-width:600px;margin:0.8rem auto 2rem;text-align:center;">Contact Blue Cap IT to deploy the spot.ai Intelligent Video Recorder. We'll handle installation, camera integration, and cloud setup.</p>
      <div style="display:flex;gap:1rem;justify-content:center;flex-wrap:wrap;">
        <a href="contact.html" class="btn-primary">Get a Free Quote</a>
        <a href="tel:4108584031" class="btn-ghost">Call (410) 858-4031</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</MainLayout>
